column1: Duck Creek Dolomite - Wilson et al. (2010)
column55: Lower ramp, slope, and deep basin
column57: Ferruginous limestone rhythmites interbedded with dolomitic turbidites, displaying well-defined Bouma sequences. Rhythmites, dolomitic turbidites, and absence of wave-influenced sedimentary structures suggest deposition in an iron-rich environment well below wave base and punctuated by turbidity currents (Wilson et al. 2010)
